  body
    // container
    .container
      .row
        div(class'twelve columns')
          h2 Welcome to Express Foundation. Using Foundation by Zurb with Node.js on Express with Jade and Stylus.
          p This is version 2.1.5 released on Januaru 26, 2012
          hr
      .row
        div(class='eight columns')
          h3 The Grid
          // Grid Example
          .row
            div(class='twelve columns')
              .panel
                p This is a twelve column section in a row. Each of these includes a div.panel element so you can see where the columns are - it's not required at all for the grid.
          .row
            div(class='six columns')
              .panel
                p Six columns
            div(class='six columns')
              .panel
                p Six columns
          .row
            div(class='four columns')
              .panel
                p Four columns
            div(class='four columns')
              .panel
                p Four columns
            div(class='four columns')
              .panel
                p Four columns
            h3 Tabs
            dl.tabs
              dd
                a(href='#simple1', class='active') Simple Tab 1
              dd
                a(href='#simple2') Simple Tab 2
              dd
                a(href='#simple3') Simple Tab 3

            ul.tabs-content
              li(class='active', id='simple1Tab') This is simple tab 1's content. Pretty neat, huh?
              li(id='simple2Tab') This is simple tab 2's content. Now you see it!
              li(id='simple3Tab') This is simple tab 3's content. It's, you know...okay.
            h3 Buttons
            p 
              a(href='#', class='small blue button') Small Blue Button
            p
              a(href='#', class='blue button') Medium Blue Button
            p
              a(href='#', class='large blue button') Large Blue Button

            p 
              a(href='#', class='nice radius small blue button') Nice Blue Button
            p
              a(href='#', class='nice radius blue button') Nice Blue Button
            p
              a(href='#', class='nice radius large blue button') Nice Blue Button
        div(class='four columns')
          h4 Getting Started
          p We're stoked you want to try Foundation! To get going, this file (index.html) includes some basic styles you can modify, play around with, or totally destroy to get going.

          h4 Other Resources
          p Once you've exhausted the fun in this document, you should check out:
          ul.disc
            li  
              a(href='http://foundation.zurb.com/docs') Foundation Documentation
              br
              | Everything you need to know about using the framework.
            li
              a(href='http://github.com/zurb/foundation') Foundation on Github</a>
              br
              | Latest code, issue reports, feature requests and more.
            li
              a(href='http://twitter.com/foundationzurb') @foundationzurb
              br
              | Ping us on Twitter if you have questions. If you build something with this we'd love to see it (and send you a totally boss sticker).
    // container
    // Included JS Files
    script(src='javascripts/jquery.min.js')
    script(src='javascripts/modernizr.foundation.js')
    script(src='javascripts/foundation.js')
    script(src='javascripts/app.js')
